<section id="Instances" remap="TID_21613">
	<title>Instances</title>
	<para>
		The <guilabel>Instance</guilabel> container combined with the ability to analyze information inside each instance provides in-depth information across the cloud environment. This rich set of information enables <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> users to improve problem resolution times and effectively manage instances in their cloud environment.
	</para>
	<para>
		The <guilabel>Instances</guilabel> pages display all instances the server discovered from your cloud providers. The <guilabel>Instances</guilabel> taskbar is a menu driven set of buttons that provide access to functions related to instances.
